title: #92Noon! Vikings Training Camp show!
description: PA is LIVE from VIkings training camps in Eagan! Featuring VEN's Gabe Henderson on Vikings talkers, the great Randy Moss calls in, Sr Defensive Asst Paul Guenther is on the perch, and a portion of Mike Zimmer's press conference to finish the show!
